Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.72,Default3,,0,0,0,,還在上課中喔
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.08,Default3,,0,0,0,,艾莉絲, 請妳出來
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.13,Default3,,0,0,0,,買給爸爸他肯定會很高興喔
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,買去當成禮物如何
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.53,Default3,,0,0,0,,那個, 少爺, 這個…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.96,Default3,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.23,Default3,,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.30,Default3,,0,0,0,,妳做得很好喔, 艾莉絲
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.61,Default3,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.20,Default3,,0,0,0,,快點告訴我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.92,0:21:57.00,Default3,,0,0,0,,春藥是什麼
